   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>LESSON SEVEN THE DEFINITION OF LIFE Scripture Reading: Eph 4:18; Rev 22:1; John 14:6a; 1 John 1:2; 5:12a; Col 3:4a; Rom 8:2a; 2 Cor 3:6b OUTLINE Life is not devotion: Devotion is our exercise of piety.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>Life is Christ living in us Gal 2:20a.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Life is not good behavior: Good behavior is our doing.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Life is Christ lived out from us Phil 1:21a.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Life is not power: Power is for work Acts 1:8.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>Life is for living John 6:57b.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Life is not gift: Gift is the ability for function Rom 12:6.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>Life is the divine being in our being John 1:13b.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>Life is not the growth in knowledge: The growth in knowledge is the increase of knowledge.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>Life is the increase of God Col 2:19b.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>Life is not our human life: Our human life bios and psuche is mortal Luke 8:43b; 21:4b; Matt 16:25-26.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>Life zoe is eternal 1 John 1:2; Psa 90:2b.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>Life is God's content and God's flowing out: God's content is God's being Eph 4:18a.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>God's flowing out is the impartation of Himself as life to us Rev 22:1.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>Life is Christ John 14:6a; Col 3:4a; 1 John 5:12a: Christ is the embodiment of God who is life Col 2:9.</S>
   <S PAR='16' RSNT='1' SNO='16'>Christ is the expression of God John 1:18; Heb 1:3a.</S>
   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>Life is the Holy Spirit: The Holy Spirit is the reality of Christ John 14:16-17; 1 Cor 15:45b.</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>The Holy Spirit is the Spirit of life that gives life to us Rom 8:2a; 2 Cor 3:6b.</S>
   <S PAR='19' RSNT='1' SNO='19'>Focus: Life is the Triune God dispensed into us and living in us.</S>
   </TEXT>
